721598f-a.title: Manhattan: Manhattan Avenue - 104th Street
721598f-a.text:
Manhattan Avenue, north from 104th Street. On the north side in the
background are the Alcazar and Parkway apartment builcings,
occupying the block from 109th to 110th Streets. The 11Gth Street
curve of the Ninth Avenue Elcvated may be seen to the right and
beyond them.
October 25, 1927.
P. L. Sperr, Photographer.
